{"tid":410160,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"佢喺咪鐘意我","createTime":"2017-09-22T16:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T17:11:22.000Z","uid":149162,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9956400209fd27b37ea476292c727857038b35c0","tid":410160,"uid":149162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:11:17.000Z","msg":"男朋友同前度分咗手成年<br />\n同我一齊時仲有聯絡<br />\n應承過我會斷聯絡<br />\n因為前度有抑鬱所以五斷住<br />\n後尾呃我話同男仔去旅行<br />\n第一次偷睇手機先知喺同前度去<br />\n嗰時我仲要借錢俾佢去<br />\n我踢爆咗佢<br />\n佢話喺為左我<br />\n想同前度一次過講清楚而去<br />\n<br />\n究竟喺咪玩法<br />\n喺咪我五識玩<br />\n喺咪我太易信人<br />\n點解佢可以咁對我<br />\n我究竟喺啲乜嘢<br />\n已經好攰<br />\n好難忘記一個我信任嘅人去背叛咗我<br />\n叫我仲點去愛你"},{"pid":"cab19bab9a046100c9a969bc89dca4b2522eb08a","tid":410160,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:12:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6df6ab8d253b771fbbd15bf54a23081d9d40cb83","tid":410160,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"喺你老母"},{"pid":"ad14338e324aa3b1c3ed865dc43774cfc0420b8d","tid":410160,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:12:54.000Z","msg":"又開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0267831f880b7a37157b0efe7fd282857aadf48e","tid":410160,"uid":137847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:13:09.000Z","msg":"五乜嘢都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f744b61cab97099f286412f5471299888abe16e","tid":410160,"uid":137847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:13:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid